
#### Expected behavior
I tried to create a password when we have to change the user name but that feature does not work.

#### Actual behavior
Lenphone this app does not work well, I want to create a password when we change the user name but it can not. I've tried repeatedly but still can not. this really does not work.

#### How to reproduce
* Open Linphone
* Click settings
* Click Password (enter the password) click ok
* This password is used when we change the user name
* But when we change the user name, password is not working
* Browser: Linphone App version 3.3.2
* Operating system: Android 7.0
